description:
In this SFJAZZ interview, vibraphone legend Bobby Hutcherson talks about how to best listen back to yourself. Check out more video shorts with the NEA Jazz Master, former SFJAZZ Collective member and long-time San Francisco native!

For more videos, subscribe today to the SFJAZZ YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/SFJAZZOnline
